Mevalonate begins with the conversion of Acetyl-CoA to HMG-CoA and ends with the conversion of Farnesyl-PP to Squalene
Sterol pathway starts with the conversion of 2,3-Oxidosqualene to Lanosterol and ends with the synthesis of Cholesterol
Isoprenylation pathway starts with the conversion of Mevalonate-5-phosphate to Farnesyl-PP and ends with the prenylation of Rac, Rho or Rab with a geranylgeranyl moiety of Geranylgeranyl-PP
